ed="T" n="0865a06"/><persName key="A011809">釋懷玉</persName>，姓<name>高</name>，<placeName key="PL000000012388">丹丘</placeName>人也。執持律法，名節峭<lb
ed="T" n="0865a07"/>然。一食<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2000"/>長坐，蚤虱恣生，唯一布衣，行懺悔之<lb
ed="T" n="0865a08"/>法課<ptr target="#n3022"/>。其一日念<persName key="A002843">彌陀佛</persName>五萬口，通誦《彌陀<lb
ed="T" n="0865a09"/>經》三十萬卷<ptr target="#n3023"/>。至<date key="j19922691992269" when-iso="+0742-07-19"><name>天寶</name>元年六月九日</date>，俄見西<lb
ed="T" n="0865a10"/>方聖像數若恒沙，有一人擎白銀臺，從窓<lb
ed="T" n="0865a11"/>而入。<persName key="A011809">玉</persName>云：「<ref type="person" target="#A011809">我</ref>合得金臺。」銀臺却出，<persName key="A011809">玉</persName>倍虔<lb
ed="T" n="0865a12"/>志。後空聲報云：「頭上已有光暈矣。請<anchor xml:id="beg0865001"/>跏<anchor xml:id="end0865001"/>趺<lb
ed="T" n="0865a13"/>結彌陀佛印。」時佛光充室，<persName key="A011809">玉</persName>手約人退曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0865a14"/>「莫觸此光明。」至<date key="j19922731992273" when-iso="+0742-07-23">十三日</date>丑時<ptr target="#n3024"/>，再有白毫光<lb
ed="T" n="0865a15"/>現，聖眾滿空。<persName key="A011809">玉</persName>云：「若聞異香，<ref type="person" target="#A011809">我</ref>報將盡。」弟<lb
ed="T" n="0865a16"/>子<persName key="A013557">慧命</persName>問：「<ref type="person" target="#A011809">師</ref>今往何剎？」<persName key="A011809">玉</persName>以偈云：「清淨皎<lb
ed="T" n="0865a17"/>潔無塵垢，蓮華化生為父母。<ref type="person" target="#A011809">我</ref>修道來經<lb
ed="T" n="0865a18"/>十劫<ptr target="#n3025"/>，出示<placeName key="PL000000055469">閻浮</placeName>厭眾苦。一生苦行超十劫，<lb
ed="T" n="0865a19"/>永離娑婆歸淨土。」<persName key="A011809">玉</persName>說偈已，香氣盈空，海<lb
ed="T" n="0865a20"/>眾遍滿，見<persName key="A002843">阿彌陀佛</persName>、<persName key="A002803">觀音</persName>、<persName key="A006106">勢至</persName>身紫金色，共<lb
ed="T" n="0865a21"/>御金剛臺來迎。<persName key="A011809">玉</persName>含笑而終，肉身現在。後<lb
ed="T" n="0865a22"/>有讚云：「<ref type="person" target="#A011809">我師</ref>一念登初地<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1802"/>，佛國笙歌兩度<lb
ed="T" n="0865a23"/>來。唯有門前古槐樹，枝低只為挂銀臺。」一<lb
ed="T" n="0865a24"/>云是<placeName key="PL000000014901">台州</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0865002"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0865002"/>史<persName key="A012079">段懷然</persName>詩也<ptr target="#n3026"/>。</p>
